PROJECT: Social Media Sentiment Analysis

Dataset Name:
Sentiment140 Dataset

Source:
Kaggle

Source URL:
https://www.kaggle.com

File Name:
training.1600000.processed.noemoticon.csv

File Format:
CSV

Dataset Size:
227 MB

Number of Records:
1,600,000 Tweets

Description:
The dataset contains 1.6 million tweets collected from Twitter.
Each tweet is labeled with sentiment information and is used for sentiment analysis tasks.

Reason for Selection:
This dataset contains a large volume of social media data suitable for training and analyzing sentiment classification models.